パッケージ com.shimizukenta.jsonhub

クラス JsonHubToPojoParser

java.lang.Object
com.shimizukenta.jsonhub.JsonHubToPojoParser
public final class JsonHubToPojoParser
extends java.lang.Object
This class is parser, from JsonHub instance to POJO(Plain-Old-Java-Object).

To parse, parse(JsonHub, Class).

To POJO Conditions.

  • Class has public new() (arguments is 0)
  • Field is public
  • Field is not static
  • Field is not final

  • メソッドの概要

    修飾子とタイプ メソッド 説明
    static <T> T parse​(JsonHub jh, java.lang.Class<T> classOfT)
    Returns parsed POJO of classOfT from JsonHub instance.

    クラスから継承されたメソッド java.lang.Object

    equals, getClass, hashCode, notify, notifyAll, toString, wait, wait, wait

  • メソッドの詳細

    • parse

      public static <T> T parse​(JsonHub jh, java.lang.Class<T> classOfT)
      Returns parsed POJO of classOfT from JsonHub instance.

      To POJO Conditions.

      • Class has public new() (arguments is 0)
      • Field is public
      • Field is not static
      • Field is not final
      型パラメータ:
      T - Type
      パラメータ:
      jh - JsonHub instance
      classOfT - Class-of-Type
      戻り値:
      parsed POJO
      例外:
      JsonHubParseException - if parse failed
